text: Kotrike Madhusudan Guptahttp://myneta.info/ap09/candidate.php?candidate_id=1964 is an Indian politician who was the 2009 Congress MLA from Guntakal for the Andhra Pradesh Legislative Assembly. He was once a member of the Indian National Congress, and now contesting as Guntakal MLA for the 2019 Andhra Pradesh Legislative Assembly election from Jana Sena Party. ==References== Category:Living people Category:Members of the Andhra Pradesh Legislative Assembly Category:People from Anantapur district Category:Jana Sena Party politicians Category:1968 births
title: Kotrike Madhusudan Gupta
